$interpreted: Cruel Bandit: Is that it?
Dumb Bandit: Look at all those gem rocks on its back. We could eat, drink and be merry for a whole year if we got our hands on those.
Cruel Bandit: Dumbass. Gem rocks from a living golem are worth even more. I'd say we could kick it for at least 5 years no sweat!
Dumb Bandit: Alright boys, let's hit him while he's down!
Golemwalt: Grrrooouuu~!!
Reinforcement Bandit: The hell, you guys aren't done with him yet?
Cruel Bandit: Quit yappin' and start helping!
Cruel Bandit: Knock him out!
Golemwalt: Grrrooouuu~!
Vanessa: Stop!
Cruel Bandit: Who's that!?
Vanessa: Get away from Golemwalt!
Dumb Bandit: Are you nuts? This thing's our golden ticket!
Reinforcement Bandit: Listen you dumb broad, either you stay out of our way, or we bury you together with this golem.
Vanessa: Looks like 'this broad' has to teach you scum some manners!
Golemwalt: Grrou~?
Cruel Bandit: The hell'd you just do!?
Vanessa: Called for help. There's a unit patrolling Sunshine Ridge nearby. They'll be here any minute now.
Cruel Bandit: Dammit!
Dumb Bandit: Don't think you're off the hook so easy!
Vanessa: Whew~ that was close. Good thing they really bought that I called for help... I guess men never can really tell when a woman's lying.
Golemwalt: Grrou~~
Vanessa: Are you okay? Sorry, I shouldn't have left you here alone.
Golemwalt: Grrou~~
Vanessa: Let's get out of here first. I'm sure they'll return once they realize no one's actually on their way.
Vanessa: Whew~ let's take a breather. It should be safe now.
Golemwalt: Grrou~~
Vanessa: What's the matter? I'm fine, see for yourself.
Vanessa: See, no limbs missing, all perfectly attached.
Golemwalt: Grrou~~
Vanessa: Haha, yes. We can sit together and rest.
Vanessa: You're so thoughtful, Golemwalt... just like the real Walt...
? ? ?: Vanessa...
? ? ?: Vanessa, over here...
